grade_preconditions.et:
In order to pass the course, a student has to:
1) Participate in at least 20 classes;
2) Hand in all homeworks on time;
3) Write all texts on time;
4) Pass all small and big tests;
5) Participate well in all speaking classes.
6) Work well in Moodle

grade_evaluation.et:
Test I: 10 points;
Test II: 10 points;
Test III: 10 points;
Text "Tore inimene": 5 points +speaking class: 5 points;
